        <Parent_String>pikes (spears) [300037033], spears by form [300213395], spears (weapons) [300037038], staff weapons [300180692], edged weapons [300036973], armaments [300420324], weapons [300036926], Weapons and Ammunition (hierarchy name) [300036743], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
